EDUCATIONAL STATEMENT:
This project is developed for educational purposes to:
- Teach cybersecurity concepts and password security
- Demonstrate responsible security research practices
- Provide hands-on learning opportunities in a controlled environment
- Promote ethical hacking and responsible disclosure practices

ETHICAL COMMITMENT:
The developers of this software are committed to promoting ethical use of security
tools and responsible disclosure practices. We encourage users to:
- Use this tool only for legitimate and authorized purposes
- Respect privacy and security of others
- Follow responsible disclosure guidelines
- Contribute to the cybersecurity community in a positive manner

By using this software, you agree to use it responsibly and ethically, in compliance
with all applicable laws and regulations, and for educational purposes only.

